  "texts": [
    "Time savings, insight into one's health, and reduced administrative burden are among the primary advantages provided by eHealth [4][5][6][7].",
    "According to a report presented by Statista in August 2022 (as shown in Fig. 1), the use of eHealth in various healthcare sectors is also expanding] (https:// www.",
    "com/ outlo ok/ dmo/ digit al-health/ eheal th/ world wide# reven ue).",
    "However, eHealth services have not developed as much as anticipated, partly due to issues of dependability, fault tolerance, and privacy.",
    "In eHealth, biological data collected by IoT devices is transmitted to Cloud entities operated by third parties, which presents challenges for data security and the protection of a patient's privacy [8][9][10][11][12].In eHealth, the wireless body area network (WBAN) is employed extensively."
  ]
